item.title: CVE-2023-43757|2024-08-02T19:52:10.967Z -- elecom%20co.%2Cltd. -- wrc-2533ghbk2-t
item.description: Inadequate encryption strength vulnerability in multiple routers provided by ELECOM CO.,LTD. and LOGITEC CORPORATION allows a network-adjacent unauthenticated attacker to guess the encryption key used for wireless LAN communication and intercept the communication. As for the affected products/versions, see the information provided by the vendor under [References] section.
